snippet.title: Pranshu Tople
snippet.description:
Hey! 
I am Pranshu Tople, a Mechatronics Engineer from Pune, MH, India 🇮🇳

I create all sorts of fun, cool & easy to understand projects in Robotics, ROS, Computer Vision, AI/ML, AR/VR/MR, etc.
You name it, & we can get it done 😉

I started this channel long back just for fun but now as I have learned so much from YouTube, I want to give back to the community.
On this channel, you can find videos that'll help you learn concepts right from scratch. 

Your major takeaways from this channel would be understandable, rememberable and useful information about - 
• Arduino, Raspberry Pi & more.
• ROS - Robot Operating System.
• Basic Robotics & Robot programming.
• AR/VR - Augmented Reality / Virtual Reality.
• Computer Vision, AI/ML
& many more Fun-to-do projects for beginners as well as experts.

For any doubts or inquiries, you can find my contact info below...
